Requirements
------------------------------------------------------
	- gtk+ ( >= 2.1.x )
	- Xlib, Xpm, gdk-pixbuf
	- root access for install

Installation
------------------------------------------------------
1) Untar/gunzip sources
	$ tar zxvf cnslock-x.x.x.tar.gz

2) Compilation
	'make'
	become root (via 'su')
	'make install'
